@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
left to right direction

title Doggy - High-Level Component Diagram

actor User

rectangle "Tier 1 - Presentation" as T1 {
  component "Web Client\n(React + Vite)" as Web
}

rectangle "Tier 2 - Application/API" as T2 {
  component "Backend API\n(FastAPI)" as Api
}

rectangle "Tier 3 - AI Services" as T3 {
  component "Dog Recognition Module\n(in-process ML)" as DogRec
  component "LLM Advice Service\n(Hugging Face Inference)" as LLM
}

User --> Web : Upload image / view result
Web --> Api : HTTP POST /api/dog-from-photo
Api --> DogRec : in-process: is_dog(image), predict(image)
Api --> LLM : generate_advice(breed)
Api --> Web : JSON {breed, advice, raw_predictions}
@enduml
